song_name: Theyre In Love Where Am I
Theyre In Love Where Am I
version_description: This tab adds the correct capo positioning for the song. This version fixes some timing issues with the words and makes it easier to follow along with the song. It also fixes a major issue with the order of the chords. Other versions on the web have Em before Bm in all the verses. Previous versions all over the internet have this wrong. This tab has also added the intro and labeled all the parts of the song.
The majority of this song is just alternating between a G and a C or Cmaj7. Pretty simple. Listen to get a feel for the rhythm: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4-xKfyhbtFk.
This is probably flawed but there is no other tab for this song. I really hope someone can take what I got and make it better but I am very tired.
Capo 4, listen along here for the rhythm: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LFvEXVrvuzg.
It is actually correct. The others are all close, but wrong.
